```
#그림생성
fig=plt.figure()
fig.set_size_inches(10,10)
import numpy as np
X_1=range(100)# 점의 개수가 같아야한다
Y_1=[np.cos(i) for i in X_1]

X_2=range(100)
Y_2=[np.sin(i) for i in X_1]
#그래프 생성
ax_1 = fig.add_subplot(1,2,1)
ax_2 = fig.add_subplot(1,2,2)
ax_1.plot(X_1,Y_1)
ax_2.plot(X_2,Y_2)
plt.show()

```
